{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2023}} {{Infobox officeholder | name = Saajidha Mohamed | image = [[File:Saajidha.png|thumb|right]] | caption = | office = [[First Lady of the Maldives]] | native_name = ސާޖިދާ މުހައްމަދު | termstart = 17 November 2023 | term_label = Assumed role | spouse = Mohamed muizzu | children = 3 | president = Mohamed muizzu | preceding = Fazna ahmed | birth_place = [[Malé]], Maldives | honorific_prefix = Madam | succeeded = | term_end = }} '''Saajidha''' '''ސާޖިދާ މުހައްމަދު''' Is the wife of the president of the Maldives, Mohamed muizzu as of 2023. In their marriage they got 3 children. Saajidha mohamed and president muizzu's office palace is muliaage (palace) (henveyru gan'duvaru which was built by sultan Shamsuddeen lll of the Maldives for his son.

