'''Ahmed Nareesh''' is the Deputy Mayor of [[Malé]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=Ahmed Nareesh |url=https://malecity.gov.mv/en/council/2 |access-date=2023-11-21 |website=Undercurrent News}}</ref> He is serving as the acting mayor, since former Mayor [[Mohamed Muizzu]] resigned On 17 November 2023.{{citation needed}}

