==Mayor of Malé City==
He was elected as the Deputy mayor on 21/6/2021. He was then-opposition [[Progressive Party of Maldives|PPM]]'s council Member. when Nareesh won the mayor elections, he was [[Maafannu]] Medhu Constituency member for [[People's Majlis]]. He Active in the [[Politics of the Maldives]] since He was a council Member of [[Progressive Party of Maldives]]

